{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/extras/Banner_Story.png?t=1736550915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You arrive in a strange place surrounded by unfamiliar faces. You and 14 others are made to compete  in a series of challenges, hosted by a mysterious woman called Lady Luck. What is the goal of this ordeal? Why do you feel like merely an observer?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/extras/tr_open.gif?t=1736550915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lady Luck proclaims these 15 strangers to be 'thieves', and for that reason, she has brought them here to fight for their lives. To survive they must complete all of Lady Luck's Challenges. Unravel the truth of Lady Luck's game, and find your way out of this strange new world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/extras/tr_cutscene.gif?t=1736550915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/extras/Banner_Features.png?t=1736550915\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    A story of secrets and deception</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Unique and dynamic puzzles to solve </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    1st-Person gameplay with fully explorable 3D escape rooms </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/extras/tr_talk.gif?t=1736550915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/extras/Banner_Gameplay.png?t=1736550915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thief's Roulette is a 1st-person puzzle adventure game with a cryptic story to unravel. At the core of the game are a series of challenges conducted by Lady Luck. You will face a large variety of puzzles and obstacles as you make your way to the truth. Thief's Roulette is not a traditional visual novel, but does feature VN style cutscenes and conversations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/extras/tr_puzzle1.gif?t=1736550915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/extras/tr_puzzle.gif?t=1736550915\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1287170?t=1736550915","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1736550915","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736550915","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736550915","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Game contains darker themes and mature language. "},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1287170/extras/Banner_Story.png?t=1736550915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You arrive in a strange place surrounded by unfamiliar faces. You and 14 others are made to compete  in a series of challenges, hosted by a mysterious woman called Lady Luck. What is the go